    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA62-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu muṉṉoru kālattup (EV: camayam) poruḷvayiṉ pirintu vanta talaivaṉ piṉṉum poruḷ valikka paṭṭa (EV: mīṇṭum poruḷmēṟ ceṉṟa) neñciṟkuc celavu aḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how HE, who at an earlier time had come [back] after separating for the sake of wealth, prevents [his] heart from going when it again coveted wealth.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA62">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            vērpiṇi vetirttuk kālporu naralicai</l>
<l>            kantupiṇi yāṉai yayarvuyirt taṉṉa</l>
<l>            veṉṟūḻ nīṭiya vēypayi laḻuvattuk</l>
<l>            kuṉṟūr matiya nōkki niṉṟuniṉain</l>
<l>            tuḷḷiṉe ṉallaṉō yāṉē muḷḷeyiṟṟut </l>
<l>            tilakan taiiya tēṅkamaḻ tirunuta</l>
<l>            lematu muṇṭōr matināṭ ṭiṅka</l>
<l>            ḷuraṟukural vevvaḷi yeṭuppa niḻaṟapa</l>
<l>            vulavai yākiya maratta</l>
<l>            kalpiṟaṅku māmalai yumparaḵ teṉavē.</l>
            </lg>
       <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent">Standing in thought, looking at the moon creeping up the hill</l>
<l rend="indent">with a rustling depth of bamboo, when the sun lengthened,</l>
<l rend="indent">sighing like an elephant fettered to a post lying down</l>
<l rend="indent">to the calling sound of dashing wind, entangled roots trembling,</l>
<l>did I not remember?</l>
<l rend="indent3">“There is a new-moon</l>
<l rend="indent">to the perceptive mind, all ours – the honey-scented</l>
<l rend="indent">fragrant forehead wearing the Tilakam of [her with] thorn teeth.</l>
<l rend="indent">It [is] beyond the stone-glittering great mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">of trees that have become [just] bare twigs so that</l>
<l rend="indent">[their] shade fails when the hot wind rouses [them] with</l>
<l rend="indent2">muttering voice.”</l>

<lg type="alternate" sameAs="1B">
    <l>... wind dashing at the bamboo with entangled roots,</l>
</lg>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="4B">
    <l>Standing in thought, looking at the moon on the hill village</l>
</lg>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="7B">
    <l>... "There is a new-moon, a moon [I] know,</l>
 </lg>
        </lg>
